{"tid":542282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貢茶列港澳台為「國家」遭舉報 中國網民怒吼：罷飲！","createTime":"2018-01-27T10:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T06:04:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":206,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c8eee8817ec1fe1b3a224f563d6c36cf2a1eeb","tid":542282,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517036486_02b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517036486_02b9.jpg&h=4c893c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517037793_38ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517037793_38ea.jpg&h=1fdee669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地早前指萬豪酒店集團一個問卷調查活動，將港澳台列為「國家」，即遭官民夾擊圍攻。近日，來自台灣的貢茶亦被揭犯上同樣的「死罪」，其日文官網有段文字把台灣形容成國家，網頁上的港澳台竟與中國並列。這次內地網民當然不會放過機會群起攻之，直言要進行杯葛罷飲。<br />\n<br />\n中國「觀察者網」報道，內地網友發現貢茶日文官網將台灣列為國家，且在官網首頁寫了一段話：「台灣了解一切品茶的方式和喝茶的樂趣，（貢茶）就是從這個國家&mdash;台灣傳來。這就是台灣茶&mdash;貢茶。」在貢茶官網「全球貢茶」的標籤下選擇「亞洲」，則可看到其直接將台灣、香港、澳門與中國並列，而非中國大陸。<br />\n網頁資料即時挑動內地網民神經，網友紛紛留言表示要拒喝「貢茶」，還說這間企業賺大陸人的錢卻把台灣列為國家，「看來是不想做生意了」。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\nCc艾熙妞兒cC：準備抵制了<br />\n<br />\n米加貝Kennedy：上頭作死，線下加盟做生意的可就慘了<br />\n<br />\n譚惜言惜言：又一個嫌命長的<br />\n<br />\n孤獨世界的夢想家：既然在中國開店，想賺中國人的錢，就要遵守中國的法律和規矩！<br />\n<br />\n李熱學：黑名單裡又一個<br />\n<br />\n嘶嘶嘶嘶正傳：貢茶再見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180127/large/1517037532_8298.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180127%2Flarge%2F1517037532_8298.jpg&h=52f519e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/201801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F201801&d=7OokyB%2F3QRM7rQz4CQKcnk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=85688483\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F201801&h=acf75b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/201801</a>"},{"pid":"32ba0953caf556d2867f48bac50f87cc8870375b","tid":542282,"uid":50506,"like":513,"dislike":3,"score":510,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"D支那狗真係好煩<br />\n成撚日係到吠<br />\n有瘋狗症就去打針啦"},{"pid":"3476f9a5aa8f9660dfccbe396a2bbd78ad61e20c","tid":542282,"uid":89530,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"玻璃心到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7aeef9f5eddd7de453038be7122fda26db50fb","tid":542282,"uid":85163,"like":4,"dislike":73,"score":-69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48fdb7a90733e4d17223596e213fe049cf420b63","tid":542282,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"記得之前好似有圖貢茶(定第二間台式飲品店)係中國show嘅台灣國旗係中國+台灣國旗混合體嚟。<br />\n有冇巴打知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2092626db617a31beeac1517fffc2b6d104262d","tid":542282,"uid":87363,"like":179,"dislike":1,"score":178,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"大陸自己有間嘢叫御品貢茶<br />\n用原本貢茶個logo<br />\n然後加御品兩隻字喺隔離扮曬係同一間公司<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思離左題<br />\n但我覺得侵權仲可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf92512f1af455545cc15108f8250a1375b1ac9","tid":542282,"uid":87363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48fdb7a90733e4d17223596e213fe049cf420b63","tid":542282,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"記得之前好似有圖貢茶(定第二間台式飲品店)係中國show嘅台灣國旗係中國+台灣國旗混合體嚟。<br />\n有冇巴打知我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201